<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA526_05_IH_0004_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <script src="./../../common_practice/js/ema526_05_ih_0003.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema526_05.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema526_05_ih_0004">
      <section class="title type2">
        <i class="icon_creative" lang="y"><span>창</span><span>의</span></i>
        <h2 data-head="4" class="is_star" lang="y">일이 일어날 가능성에 알맞은 일을 주변에서 한 가지씩 찾아 써 보세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="flex justify_center">
          <div class="table_wrap">
            <table>
              <thead>
                <tr>
                  <th lang="y">가능성</th>
                  <th lang="y">일</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <th lang="y">~일 것 같다</th>
                  <td>
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field></math-field>
                      <div class="example_box">
                        <p lang="y">주사위 한 개를 던졌을 때 나온 주사위 눈의 수는 2 이상일 것입니다.</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <th lang="y">확실하다</th>
                  <td>
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field></math-field>
                      <div class="example_box">
                        <p lang="y">11월의 다음 달은 12월일 것입니다.</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <p lang="y">주변에서 일이 일어날 가능성에 알맞은 일을 찾아봅니다.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- <div class="buttons_solve">
                  
              </div> -->
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnSubmit">전송</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
